31
00:01:53,360 --> 00:01:57,940
By the way, what are we?

32
00:01:59,180 --> 00:02:01,320
What do you mean by that?

33
00:02:01,320 --> 00:02:05,690
Just... What am I to you?

34
00:02:05,690 --> 00:02:10,090
A debtor. A twenty-year-old debtor.

35
00:02:13,390 --> 00:02:17,780
Then, what do you think of me?

36
00:02:17,780 --> 00:02:24,960
You? Hm, a parasite that lives in my rooftop house.

37
00:02:26,900 --> 00:02:29,120
Your words are harsh.

38
00:02:29,120 --> 00:02:32,350
Calling me a centipede that lives in your rooftop house would've been better!

39
00:02:33,790 --> 00:02:37,820
Sure, you can be a centipede then.

40
00:02:38,800 --> 00:02:40,720
- Bro.
- Yeah?

41
00:02:40,720 --> 00:02:45,080
Can I go visit the office you live in?

42
00:02:52,280 --> 00:02:55,530
We should've gone back home instead. Why did you want to come here?

43
00:02:55,530 --> 00:03:00,280
I mean, you're always at my house tormenting me,

44
00:03:00,280 --> 00:03:03,400
so I wanted to come to your home and be a nuisance, too.

45
00:03:06,650 --> 00:03:09,200
Where do you sleep?

46
00:03:09,200 --> 00:03:10,630
There.

47
00:03:10,630 --> 00:03:12,650
Here?

48
00:03:23,890 --> 00:03:26,030
It's more comfortable than I thought it would be.

49
