59
00:04:27,130 --> 00:04:30,010
A magical moment that confirms your love.

60
00:04:30,010 --> 00:04:34,120
Your first kiss can tell you everything.

61
00:05:07,430 --> 00:05:09,400
I like you.

62
00:05:28,150 --> 00:05:30,120
I'm sorry.

63
