♫ Even if I lived for only a day, I'd want to be by your side ♫

72
00:06:33,990 --> 00:06:40,490
♫ If one step could only bring me closer to you ♫

73
00:06:40,490 --> 00:06:46,790
♫ I wish and wish for the day ♫

74
00:06:46,790 --> 00:06:49,440
♫  where I can be in love with you ♫

75
00:06:49,440 --> 00:06:53,640
I'm going to sleep alone at home today. You should go.

76
00:06:53,640 --> 00:06:56,110
You said it was our home.

77
00:06:58,860 --> 00:07:01,550
Who's the one who drew the line?

78
00:07:05,710 --> 00:07:13,170
I'm going to win first place and make it so that we can start over again.

79
00:07:14,190 --> 00:07:16,190
So, you should go now.

80
00:07:20,250 --> 00:07:22,150
Goodnight.

81
00:07:30,500 --> 00:07:37,540
♫ I want to love you, so why can't I? ♫

82
00:07:37,540 --> 00:07:45,600
♫ Even if I live for only a day, I want it to be by your side ♫

83
00:07:45,600 --> 00:07:53,460
