92
00:08:30,320 --> 00:08:33,420
♫ Closer to you ♫

93
00:08:33,420 --> 00:08:39,640
♫ I wish and wish for the day  ♫

94
00:08:39,640 --> 00:08:45,030
♫ Where I can be in love with you ♫

95
00:09:18,610 --> 00:09:20,580
I'll return after winning first place.

96
00:09:20,580 --> 00:09:25,910
If I get first place, then our debtor-creditor relationship won't be a problem anymore.

97
00:09:26,730 --> 00:09:28,640
