98
00:09:28,640 --> 00:09:30,800
Mr. Song Shi On, it's your turn to go in.

99
00:09:30,800 --> 00:09:32,550
Yes.

100
00:09:40,750 --> 00:09:44,470
Stay right there, don't go anywhere.

