104
00:10:44,200 --> 00:10:48,350
So that's the end of our debtor-creditor relationship, isn't it?

105
00:10:52,620 --> 00:10:54,530
- Shi On.
- Yes?

106
00:10:54,530 --> 00:10:56,950
How did you dance?

107
00:10:56,950 --> 00:10:58,910
Are you curious?

108
00:10:58,910 --> 00:11:02,550
If you're curious, you can throw me a celebration party then.

109
